    "Title": "~mission(ReputationRank) Hauler Needed for Direct ~mission(CargoGradeToken) Shipment",
    "DisplayTitle": "Rookie Hauler Needed for Direct Bulk Shipment",
    "Description": "RED WIND LINEHAUL\n'YOUR GOODS IN GOOD HANDS'\n----------------------------\n\nGot a contract from a major client who needs a skilled pilot to move a large load of luxury items from <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4> to <EM4>~mission(Destination|Address)</EM4>. \n\nYou'll need room for at least <EM4>~mission(MissionMaxSCUSize) cargo containers</EM4> in your hold. You'll also need a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> to get everything loaded and unloaded. \n\nAnd as a fair warning, the things you'll be carrying are pricey enough that you might attract some unwanted attention. <EM4>Be ready to defend yourself</EM4> if you can't evade.",
    "DisplayDescription": "RED WIND LINEHAUL\n'YOUR GOODS IN GOOD HANDS'\n----------------------------\n\nGot a contract from a major client who needs a skilled pilot to move a large load of luxury items from <EM4>[Location|Address]</EM4> to <EM4>Teasa Spaceport</EM4>. \n\nYou'll need room for at least <EM4>8 SCU cargo containers</EM4> in your hold. You'll also need a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> to get everything loaded and unloaded. \n\nAnd as a fair warning, the things you'll be carrying are pricey enough that you might attract some unwanted attention. <EM4>Be ready to defend yourself</EM4> if you can't evade.",
